title: Bie Re Liumang Tu Ma Xiu
synopsis: What kind of hilarious story will be brought about by the strong return of the ancestor of the cheap and cute rogue rabbit? The first generation of Internet celebrity rogue rabbits are incarnations of "black sesame glutinous rice balls"-the black-bellied soul is hidden under the appearance of Bai Ruanmeng, and the strength interprets what is "soft-cute" black-bellied. The plot of the ghost horse, the funny action and the wonderful soundtrack reinterpret the daily life of the rogue rabbit Matthew and his friends. See how the cute and cute rogue rabbit sets off a new round of hilarious rabbit whirlwind... (translated from iqiyi)
